description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;North Bristol NHS Trust are seeking experienced project managers to join the Digital Project Management Team. This is an exciting opportunity and a great time to join an experienced team who have an excellent reputation for successful project delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;North Bristol Trust are embarking on a Digital Transformation Programme that sees the organisation transition from using paper based solutions to digital tools and systems and these project management roles are pivotal to successful implementation and deployment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our team are dynamic and you will also be expected to work across Bristol North Somerset South Gloucester (BNSSG) to deliver System wide digital change.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;There are a variety of System Change projects and the post holder will need to be able to manage multiple projects, lead a diverse project team and provide the project management leadership and expertise to see the projects through from Business Case production, through effective procurement and successful deployment and handover.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;These roles are initial 12 months fixed term contracts but there may be an opportunity to extend further.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The interview process will consist of screening via MS Teams and if successful an interview via MS Teams with a presentation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;PREVIOUS APPLICANTS NEED NOT APPLY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information please contact;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Chelsey.Gilmour@nbt.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
